# Example output files and folders (generated by running examples).
# NOTE: sample INPUT files are named input*.<ext> — Merger examples take .txt and
# .jpg inputs too, so the broad rules below would wrongly ignore them. The negations
# at the end re-include every input* file and every *.py script, so only generated
# scratch outputs stay ignored. (These rules were inherited from a product whose
# example outputs were text/markdown only, which is why the collision exists.)
Examples/**/*.md
Examples/**/*.txt
Examples/**/output/
Examples/**/content/
Examples/**/images/*
Examples/**/output.pdf
!Examples/**/input*
!Examples/**/*.py

